{"id":222822,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/04/北邮校长指责日本媒体造谣，表示将追究责任/","date":"2012-04-27T04:33:52Z","modified":"2012-04-27T04:33:52Z","title":"北邮校长指责日本媒体造谣，表示将追究责任","content":"<p>《纽约时报》报导北邮校长方滨兴参与了薄王的监听系统建设，而《读卖新闻》则引用消息来源发表简短新闻，称方校长被双规被拘。数个月没有在微博上留言的北邮校长进行辟谣，但只指责《读卖》造谣，未回应NYT的报道。 方滨兴说，“我这两天作为组长在评审‘千人计划’，却被读卖新闻给‘消失了’。消失我者加藤隆则竟是读卖新闻总局长，令人大跌眼镜。《读卖新闻》戏弄中国网民的智商，应该及时向我及中国网民道歉，才不失主流报刊的风范。否则我要问，你们登载新闻的谣言率是多少？不要说是0%，因为这必定是谣言！”前谷歌中国总裁李开复说，“追究麻烦，墙了它吧！”方回应“好汉不提当年勇啊，不在其位不谋其政，现在只能追究了”。<img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/1ec82669/mf.gif\" border=\"0\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/viral/sendEmail.cfm?lang=en&amp;title=%E5%8C%97%E9%82%AE%E6%A0%A1%E9%95%BF%E6%8C%87%E8%B4%A3%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%AA%92%E4%BD%93%E9%80%A0%E8%B0%A3%EF%BC%8C%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E5%B0%86%E8%BF%BD%E7%A9%B6%E8%B4%A3%E4%BB%BB&amp;link=http%3A%2F%2Finternet.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D12%2F04%2F27%2F0125235%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/04/260f6417emailthis2.gif.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E5%8C%97%E9%82%AE%E6%A0%A1%E9%95%BF%E6%8C%87%E8%B4%A3%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%AA%92%E4%BD%93%E9%80%A0%E8%B0%A3%EF%BC%8C%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E5%B0%86%E8%BF%BD%E7%A9%B6%E8%B4%A3%E4%BB%BB&amp;link=http%3A%2F%2Finternet.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D12%2F04%2F27%2F0125235%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/04/044291a1bookmark.gif.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/132995904210/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/1ec82669/a2.htm\"><img src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/132995904210/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/1ec82669/a2.img\" border=\"0\" /></a><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://pi.feedsportal.com/r/132995904210/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/1ec82669/a2t